          "inYear": 3
        }
      },
      "message": "Asset created successfully with purchase and warranty records"
    },
    "keyPoints": [
      "fixedAsset._id is the main asset identifier (use for future updates)",
      "purchase & warranty both reference fixedAsset._id as 'assetId'",
      "purchase will be null if no purchase fields were provided",
      "warranty will be null if no warranty fields were provided",
      "All 3 collections are separate and independently queryable",
      "From now on, you can GET /assets/:id with fixedAsset._id to retrieve full asset with purchase/warranty"
